<br>
Used a Water pet myself but Earth is probably a better choice.  His 6/7 min spawn time is almost perfect as a med break and pet heal time.  As soon as he would pop regardless of mana I would DS pet and Malise pull.  He WILL cast SoW on himself (or its the ogre chick in the house) on about his 3rd spell I saw.  He casts Scourge as a DoT and does hit fairly hard.   Like I said though, DS - Malise - back up till pet has agro - heal pet after 2 ticks - Nuke Nuke Nuke.  Personally I found OT to be a bit better, and you'll be able to solo there in a couple levels if not now.<br>
<br>
