<br>
I used earthpet, and had a timer setup to know when he was going to pop.  About 1 minute before pop, I'd DS the pet and rebuff.  Med until he popped, then while he was trying to cast his first buff...send pet and nuke him until he was dead.  Speed is the key...I think in all the times I killed him, he only got is Scourge spell off twice.<br>
<br>
